modName: Daedric Armor variation of Killer Keos Skimpy CBBE V2 Armor

descriptionHtml:
This is a variation of the Daedric Armor in Killer Keos Skimpy CBBE V2 Armor Set. (link [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=3654]here[/url])

[b]=== Update 1.1 ===[/b]
- Added weight slider option which affects breast and bottom sizes (you can press [b]~[/b] to open up the console and type in [b]showracemenu[/b] to change your current character\'s weight)
- Added normals for lighting

[b]=== Description ===[/b]
Changes made to original KillerKeo\'s armor:
- Bustier breasts
- Nipples revealed
- Armor made slightly more fitted around the base model (less gap space)
